Subject:IMPORTANT INFORMATION REGARDING YOUR STARBUCKS CARD SUBSCRIPTION

Thank you for using your Starbucks Card. The following message
provides information regarding your Starbucks Card Automatic Reload account.


*** UNABLE TO OBTAIN AUTHORIZATION ON THE CREDIT CARD OR PAYPAL ACCOUNT ASSOCIATED WITH THIS
AUTOMATIC RELOAD ACCOUNT. ***

We are unable to obtain authorization on the credit card or PayPal account associated with
this account. As a result, Automatic Reload has been suspended on this 
account. If you would like to associate a different payment method with your 
automatic reload account, please perform the following steps:

1) Visit https://www.starbucks.com/account/home to sign into your
Starbucks.com account
2) Click on the "Manage My Account" button
3) Click on "Set Auto-Reload"
4) Click on "Use a different payment method"
5) Click on "edit" or "Add a new payment method"

If you have questions about your Starbucks Card account, please contact us by replying to this email or by calling us at 1-800-782-7282.
Our customer service representatives can be reached by phone Monday - Friday, 5AM - 8PM (PST).

For additional information regarding the Starbucks Card, please visit our FAQ area 
at http://www.starbucks.com/customer/faq_qanda.asp?name=card.

